=== G-11-directions: Asking for Directions (A1-A2) ===
Opening: Hi. You look a little lost. Where are you trying to go?

[normal ask]
  IN:  Excuse me, could you tell me how to get to the train station?
  OUT: Sure. Go straight for two blocks, then turn left. The station is on your right.

[short answer]
  IN:  Left.
  OUT: Turn left at the next street, and you'll see the bus stop on your right.

